name: 格蕾丝・奥莎莉雯
name_full: 格蕾丝・奥莎莉雯 Grace O'Sullivan
introduction: Grace O'Sullivan began her acting career on popular Australian soap opera Neighbours and its subsequent spin off, Erinsborough High. She is set to star in the upcoming action thriller Ice Road 2: Road to the Sky alongside Liam Neeson and Fan BingBing. The sequel, directed by Jonathan Hensleigh (writer of Jumanji and Die Hard With A Vengeance) recently wrapped filming in Victoria.
